Shingletown, CA: Mark V. Ziesing Books, 1997. First Edition. Hardcover. Item #29530

ISBN: 0929480848

Edition limited to 300 signed and numbered copies, this being #167. Signed by Eugene Byrne and Kim Newman on the limitation page. 356pp. Red cloth stamped in gold on the spine panel. Spine heel a bit bruised else a fine copy in fine dustjacket. Original slipcase is in fine condition. ; Octavo; Signed by All Authors.

Price: $125.00 save 30% $87.50
